                  "value": "Interlock 100% poliéster reciclado"
                },
                {
                  "id": "en_GB",
                  "type": "STRING",
                  "ocurrence": 0,
                  "value": "\"Clean, classic and created to mark a milestone. The timeless look of this adidas Real Madrid home jersey is accented with light purple details and a repeated club badge embossed onto the white fabric. This juniors' version is made to keep young fans comfortable with moisture-wicking AEROREADY. Made with 100% recycled materials, this product represents just one of our solutions to help end plastic waste.\""
                },
